			<div class="content" id="post-content-2111059">
									

<p>I think that I'd make a good addition to the staff team. I've been around the site for a while now, and I definitely know the in's and out's. I'm on good terms with those on the IRC chat, including other members of staff, and I uphold a neutral (if not cheery) demeanor. I am also versed in giving review, critique, and general thoughts about articles as a whole, both scip and tales; it used to be a habit of mine to post on the forum threads as much as possible, but I stay to chat most often these days. I am a great listener, and in my best place when I am able to discuss and debate with others. I'm definitely a team player.</p>
<p>As for my appearance on chat and the site &#8212; I think I can safely say that I am active for a good chunk of every day both on-site and in chat, especially the latter. As such, I can definitely consider myself highly active on the site and its affiliates, and remain very aware of ongoing events.</p>

							</div>

								
